\frac{\mathrm{d}(c\circ\psi)}{\mathrm{d}s}=K(=constant)
\nabla_{\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}s}}\frac{\mathrm{d}(c\circ\psi)}{\mathrm{d}s}=\nabla_{\frac{\mathrm{d}}{\mathrm{d}s}}K=0
